I am a lifelong car enthusiast with years of experience working in the auto industry. My experience includes sales, service, shipping/receiving and inventory management. Now I’m using my experience to make available well maintained, clean vehicles at affordable prices for your rental needs.

All of my vehicles have been hand-selected by me for their maintenance history, options, and reliability statistics for that specific make/model. 

All of my vehicles are on a strict 5k mile maintenance and inspection schedule. All work is done by my certified mechanic. 

Expect a prompt response and a pleasant experience, I try my utmost to ensure all your questions/concerns have been fully answered.
I enjoy nearly all outdoor sports and activities,  and camping.  More than that, I enjoy spending time with my family and friends.  Please reach out with any questions. Thank you for renting from me!

I'm thrilled to have the chance to share my passion for cars and travel with you.

When it comes to hosting on Turo, I believe in providing guests with a safe and seamless experience. Integrity and respect are values that I hold dear in all aspects of my life, and as your host, I strive to provide you with a safe and enjoyable experience. I believe in clear/candid communication and transparency, and I am committed to making your trip as smooth and stress-free as possible.

One of my all-time favorite travel experiences was a trip to Italy. The picturesque coastline, the quaint villages, and the mouthwatering cuisine were simply unforgettable. It was a true feast for the senses, and I'd love to help you plan a similarly memorable adventure in Denver.

When it comes to dream cars, I've always been drawn to sleek and stylish sports cars. The new sustainability EV boom is intriguing - I’m always discovering new models,and  makes that capture my imagination.

In my free time, I'm an avid outdoorsman. 
Whether I'm hiking, camping, fishing, or just taking a leisurely stroll through the woods, I find solace and rejuvenation in nature. I also enjoy practicing yoga, playing guitar, and spending quality time with my loved ones. Chelsea, our children, and our furry friend Juke are the center of my world, and I cherish every moment we spend together.

Thank you for considering me as your Turo host. I'm excited to help you plan the trip of a lifetime and create memories that will last a lifetime.

Greetings, and welcome to your Turo experience! I'm Martin Rousseau, and I'd like to take a moment to share my vision and what you can expect when you choose to embark on a journey with us.

**Why Turo?**
When I was searching for a business concept, I explored various options, including franchises. However, the significant capital requirements and long ROI timelines were a deterrent. Turo, with its innovative peer-to-peer car rental concept, stood out. It offered more flexibility and control over our investment, making it an exciting venture with a reasonable initial outlay.

**Our Fleet:**
What sets us apart is our commitment to providing you with the best. Our vehicles are all brand new, ensuring minimal maintenance and downtime. While this level of newness won't last indefinitely, it's a testament to our dedication to offering a professional, reliable fleet managed with care.

**Quality and Reliability:**
When you rent a vehicle from us, you're choosing not just a mode of transportation but a reliable companion for your journey. Our vehicles are professionally cared for, presenting a sense of professionalism from the moment you get behind the wheel. We want you to feel confident and comfortable as you explore Colorado's beautiful landscapes.

**Discover Colorado:**
Colorado is an extraordinary state, teeming with natural beauty and adventure. We invite you to explore the breathtaking landscapes, from Denver to Estes Park, Grand Lakes, Silverthorne, Breckenridge, FairPlay, Colorado Springs, and back to Denver. It's a journey filled with awe-inspiring sights and experiences, tailored to the time you have available.

**Our Mission:**
Ultimately, our mission is to ensure your visit to Colorado is unforgettable. We want you to relax, immerse yourself in the beauty of the state, and leave with cherished memories. If we can assist you in any way to make your visit more special, whether it's with recommendations, support, or any other need, consider our job well done.

We're here to make your Turo experience seamless, enjoyable, and memorable. Feel free to reach out with any questions or requests. We're excited to be part of your journey in Colorado.

Warm regards,
Martin Rousseau
